snippet.textDisplay: Sod electric cars, when they can charge up in the same time it takes to fill a petrol tank, do 600 miles on a tank of fuel I'll think about it,  until then I'm damned if I'm going to drive around looking for overpriced charging stations,  hanging around wasting hours of my time whilst the thing charges up, only to be able to do 300 miles if you're lucky.
